## Dashboard UI

Open `frontend/index.html` in your browser. No build step or extra server needed.

### Panels

| Panel | Description |
|---|---|
| **Overview** | Live stats — total indexes, documents, uptime, server status |
| **Indexes** | Create and delete indexes with custom HNSW parameters |
| **Upsert Docs** | Insert documents with dense vector, sparse vector and payload |
| **Search** | Dense or hybrid search with live payload filters |
| **Visualize** | 2D canvas projection of stored vectors colored by category |
| **AI Assistant** | Chat interface using semantic search over your data |
| **Benchmark** | Run N queries and measure avg, P95, P99 latency and QPS |
| **README Gen** | Generate and download README.md from live database state |
| **API Docs** | Interactive REST reference — try every endpoint live |

### AI Assistant Demo Queries

```
Index: conversations  →  "how to deal with stress at work"
Index: technical      →  "explain microservices vs monolith architecture"
Index: nlp-papers     →  "transformer models for text classification"
Index: movies         →  "sci-fi movies about space and humanity"
Index: products       →  "wireless electronics under $200 in stock"
```

