## API Reference

### System

```http
GET  /health           # Server health check
GET  /stats            # Full database statistics
```

### Indexes

```http
POST   /indexes                    # Create a new vector index
GET    /indexes                    # List all indexes
GET    /indexes/{name}             # Get index info
DELETE /indexes/{name}             # Delete an index
```

#### Create Index — Request Body

```json
{
  "name": "my-index",
  "dim": 128,
  "metric": "cosine",
  "M": 16,
  "ef_construction": 200
}
```

| Field | Type | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `name` | string | Unique index name |
| `dim` | integer | Vector dimension (1–4096) |
| `metric` | string | Distance metric: `cosine`, `l2`, or `ip` |
| `M` | integer | HNSW bi-directional links per node |
| `ef_construction` | integer | Build-time accuracy (higher = slower build, better recall) |

---

### Documents

```http
POST   /indexes/{name}/upsert                  # Insert or update documents
DELETE /indexes/{name}/documents/{id}          # Delete a document
```

#### Upsert — Request Body

```json
{
  "documents": [
    {
      "id": "doc-001",
      "vector": [0.12, -0.45, 0.88],
      "sparse_vector": {"ai": 0.9, "search": 0.7},
      "payload": {"category": "tech", "year": 2024, "rating": 9.1}
    }
  ]
}
```

| Field | Type | Required | Description |
|---|---|---|---|
| `id` | string | ✅ | Unique document ID |
| `vector` | float[] | ✅ | Dense embedding vector |
| `sparse_vector` | object | ❌ | Token weights for hybrid search |
| `payload` | object | ❌ | Arbitrary metadata for filtering |

---

### Search

```http
POST /indexes/{name}/search
```

#### Request Body

```json
{
  "vector": [0.12, -0.45, 0.88],
  "sparse_vector": {"ai": 0.9, "search": 0.7},
  "top_k": 10,
  "alpha": 0.7,
  "ef_search": 100,
  "filters": [
    {"field": "category", "op": "eq",  "value": "tech"},
    {"field": "rating",   "op": "gte", "value": 8.5},
    {"field": "in_stock", "op": "eq",  "value": true}
  ],
  "include_payload": true
}
```

| Field | Type | Default | Description |
|---|---|---|---|
| `vector` | float[] | required | Query embedding |
| `sparse_vector` | object | null | Sparse query tokens — enables hybrid mode |
| `top_k` | integer | 10 | Number of results to return |
| `alpha` | float | 0.7 | Hybrid blend: `1.0` = dense only, `0.0` = sparse only |
| `ef_search` | integer | 100 | Search accuracy (higher = slower, better recall) |
| `filters` | array | [] | Payload filter conditions (AND logic) |
| `include_payload` | boolean | true | Include payload in results |

#### Filter Operators

| Operator | Description | Example |
|---|---|---|
| `eq` | Equal | `{"field": "genre", "op": "eq", "value": "sci-fi"}` |
| `ne` | Not equal | `{"field": "status", "op": "ne", "value": "draft"}` |
| `gt` | Greater than | `{"field": "year", "op": "gt", "value": 2020}` |
| `gte` | Greater than or equal | `{"field": "rating", "op": "gte", "value": 8.0}` |
| `lt` | Less than | `{"field": "price", "op": "lt", "value": 100}` |
| `lte` | Less than or equal | `{"field": "price", "op": "lte", "value": 200}` |
| `in` | Value in list | `{"field": "tag", "op": "in", "value": ["AI","ML"]}` |
| `contains` | String contains | `{"field": "title", "op": "contains", "value": "neural"}` |

#### Response

```json
{
  "hits": [
    {
      "id": "doc-001",
      "score": 0.923456,
      "dense_score": 0.891234,
      "sparse_score": 0.032222,
      "payload": {"category": "tech", "year": 2024}
    }
  ],
  "total": 1,
  "query_time_ms": 2.341,
  "index": "my-index",
  "mode": "hybrid"
}
```

